1. *Plava* haljina mi se sviđa. (I like the *blue* dress.)
2. Kada se sunce pomeri ka zapadu, nebo postaje sve *plavije*. (When the sun moves towards the west, the sky becomes increasingly *bluer*.)
3. *Plave* oči su joj prelepe. (Her *blue* eyes are gorgeous.)
4. Videla sam *plavog* goluba na prozoru. (I saw a *blue* pigeon on the window.)
5. Kosa joj je *plave* boje. (Her hair is *blonde*.)
6. Zašto je voda u bazenu tako *plava*? (Why is the water in the pool so *blue*?)
7. Ona nosi *plavu* torbu. (She carries a *blue* bag.)
8. *Plavi* patlidžan se koristi u mnogim jelima. (The *blue* eggplant is used in many dishes.)
9. Nebo je danas posebno *plavo* i vedro. (The sky is particularly *blue* and clear today.)
10. Slikar je koristio različite nijanse plave boje u svom delu. (The painter used various shades of *blue* in his work.)

Note: The word "plava" in these examples is used as an adjective or a noun, and it can refer to various shades of blue, including light blue and dark blue.